{"article_id":"OowH3XG6qmfvmqJR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Al Qaedas Yemen branch is claiming responsibility for last week 's deadly attacks in Paris","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that killed 14 people ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"including three gunmen .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"In a video","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"posted online","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Nasr al-Ansi , a top leader from the group in the Arabian Peninsula , said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"the massacre at Charlie Hebdo was in vengeance for its satirical depictions of the Islamic Prophet Mohammed .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"He also said","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that France belongs to the `` party of Satan ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and warned of more tragedies and terror .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Refusing to be cowed ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Charlie Hebdo cartoonist Renald Luzier said ,","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"`` The terrorists","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"who attacked us","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"want hatred between people .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"They also want hatred between the people","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"they believe","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"they are defending . ''","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"In the wake of last weeks attacks , Frances prime minister is demanding tougher anti-terrorism measures .","depth":3},{"id":19,"text":"`` France is at war against terrorism , jihadism and radical Islam , ''","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"Prime Minister Manuel Valls said .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"Investigators say","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"the two brothers","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who massacred the staff at Charlie Hebdo","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"had accomplices","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"because the weapons","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"used in the attacks","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"came from abroad .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Now authorities in several countries are searching for those possible accomplices and the sources of financing .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"On Tuesday , authorities in Bulgaria arrested a French citizen","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"who may be linked to the two brothers","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"who attacked the magazine .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"But officials believe","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"the girlfriend of the gunman","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"who killed four people at a Jewish supermarket","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"has escaped","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"to join ISIS in Syria .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"France remains on its highest alert level this week ,","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"and security services in Britain are on high alert in the wake of the killings .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"New threats have also been aimed at U.S. airports .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"And lawyers for Boston Marathon supsect Dzhokhar Tsarnev have asked a judge to suspend jury selection in the trial for at least a month .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"They say","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"a delay would allow some time for the extraordinary prejudice","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"following for these events .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Meanwhile , the first edition of Charlie Hebdo since the terror attacks features a picture of Islams Prophet Mohammed on the front cover .","depth":3},{"id":45,"text":"It sold out at newsstands across France","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"-- within minutes of going on sale Wednesday .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":93,"left":67,"right":92,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":64,"right":66,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":56,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":56,"left":49,"right":55,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":49,"left":0,"right":48,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":48,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":52,"right":54,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"p